sequenceDiagram
    actor Admin
    participant AdminDashboard as Admin Dashboard
    participant AnalyticsController as Analytics Controller
    participant KnowledgeModel as Knowledge Model (FSRS)
    participant Database

    Note over Admin,AdminDashboard: UC-04: View Student Analytics

    Admin->>AdminDashboard: Navigates to Analytics section
    AdminDashboard->>AnalyticsController: getAggregatedMetrics()
    AnalyticsController->>Database: getReviewCount()
    Database-->>AnalyticsController: review_count

    alt review_count < 10
        AnalyticsController-->>AdminDashboard: Error: "Insufficient data for analysis"
        AdminDashboard-->>Admin: Display placeholder message & disable charts
    else Data sufficient (>= 10 reviews)
        par Query Aggregated Data
            AnalyticsController->>Database: getActiveUsers(7_30_days)
            AnalyticsController->>Database: getTopicMasteryAverages()
            Database-->>AnalyticsController: raw_engagement_and_mastery_data
        end

        AnalyticsController->>KnowledgeModel: calculateRetentionMetrics(stability_data)
        KnowledgeModel-->>AnalyticsController: estimated_retention_rates
        AnalyticsController-->>AdminDashboard: Display key metrics (Stability, Retention, Active Users)

        opt Search or Filter by Topic
            Admin->>AdminDashboard: Enters search query / Selects Topic
            AdminDashboard->>AnalyticsController: getTopicSpecificAnalytics(topicId)
            AnalyticsController->>Database: getPerformanceDistribution(topicId)
            Database-->>AnalyticsController: topic_performance_data
            AnalyticsController-->>AdminDashboard: Render interactive visualization (Bar/Trend)
            AdminDashboard-->>Admin: Updates chart view
        end

        opt Export Report
            Admin->>AdminDashboard: Clicks "Export Report" (CSV/PDF)
            AdminDashboard->>AnalyticsController: generateReport(metrics)
            AnalyticsController-->>AdminDashboard: Deliver file blob
            AdminDashboard-->>Admin: Download report
        end
    end